[02:48.50]Summer in the hills / 群山盛夏之时
[02:51.68]Those hazy days I do remember / 那雾蒙蒙的日子仍历历在目
[02:55.50]We were running still / 我们坚定的奔跑
[02:58.06]Had the whole world at our feet / 踏遍整个天下
[03:02.10]Watching seasons change / 见证季节更替
